# .ratchet/format.schema — canonical task record (PLAN.md Part A, machine form)
#
# Each task is a fenced record: a `### T-<phase>.<seq> <title>` header, rigid
# YAML-shaped fields, a `---` separator, then free prose (never parsed).
#
# Rigid fields (id through criteria_map):
#   id            T-<phase>.<seq>[<split-suffix>]
#   phase         integer, must equal the phase in the id
#   status        pending | red | green | done | split | blocked   (list.md only)
#   depends_on    [task ids]                                         resolvable
#   stack         language/runtime
#   criteria      list of `Cn: <falsifiable assertion>`             >= 1
#   not_doing     list of scope exclusions
#   test_files    [paths]                                           (list.md only)
#   criteria_map  Cn: [test names]                                  (list.md only)
#   attempts      integer                                           (list.md only)
#   last_failure  string or | block                                 (list.md only)
